                "text": "When a Swarm escutchide hits with its gore attack, it deals normal damage. If the attack roll result equals or exceeds the target\u2019s KAC + 4, the escutchide can either knock the target prone or move the target 5 feet in any direction.",
                "name": "Pummel",
